First question: What will you do with N2,730,000,000? Run the world? A man has become the most fortunate man in the world at the moment after he purchased a storage unit at an auction for N182,000($500). The unnamed man says that after he bought the unit, he decided to check it out and found a safe containing NN2,730,000,000 (7.5 million dollars). As soon as word got to the previous owners, they hired a lawyer. The two parties decided to allow the new owner take N436,800,000 (1.2 million dollars) for returning the money. Watch below: 